This is a specially selected, compact cultivar of the classic tropical green, revered across Asia for its incredible versatility and delightful crunch. ‘Aqua-Morning’ delivers the signature hollow stems and tender leaves that make water spinach a stir-fry champion, now optimized for the productivity of a hydroponic system.

